{"tid":1846992,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"咁辛苦返工托柒咩？帶到錢入棺材？","createTime":"2020-01-27T22:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T06:21:54.000Z","uid":26106,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62e1a1b1f2b0b770b372853606524eac62e60751","tid":1846992,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T22:40:27.000Z","msg":"你返工都係為錢咋嘛<br />\n聽日就成班支那人黎到香港<br />\n到時肺炎大爆發<br />\n死撚左咪又係帶唔到錢入棺材<br />\n<br />\n萬一咁好彩無病無痛<br />\n咪交稅幫班支那人埋醫院張單囉<br />\n<br />\n林鄭就係睇死唔會有人敢罷工<br />\n班死黑警OT費已經要硬食<br />\n依家班支那人既醫療費都要你地硬食埋呀<br />\n<br />\n仲返工？"},{"pid":"acadac406f2dd1eb4be15aadbac24ea3c087ca8c","tid":1846992,"uid":219721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T22:43:19.000Z","msg":"用自己錢醫完班支那人仲要用自己啲al幫自己隔離<br />\n同中出完你之後仲要妳自己出錢去夾公仔有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a810425111df1af742ff5b856add8d4d878f98","tid":1846992,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T22:47:44.000Z","msg":"算啦， 佢哋自己選擇<br />\n平時叫人珍惜生命， 但佢哋睇份工大過自己條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77de6b687d959a3a909095622a34c96b9bab665","tid":1846992,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4a810425111df1af742ff5b856add8d4d878f98","tid":1846992,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T22:47:44.000Z","msg":"算啦， 佢哋自己選擇<br />\n平時叫人珍惜生命， 但佢哋睇份工大過自己條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T22:50:05.000Z","msg":"另類花式自殺"},{"pid":"89f54ced0b661c1166d0df037cb7cba195a289b9","tid":1846992,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T22:52:06.000Z","msg":"已經全公司罷<br />\nART FREELANCE HOME OFFICE<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本我罷唔罷都無影響，返工喺屋企返就得"},{"pid":"7af5160463c7f4c153e295020769892db40b3603","tid":1846992,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T22:54:49.000Z","msg":"人為財死，一早覺得係香港做人啦知為乜，一生只係為左錢而生存，好多人都未享受過人生就入棺材，死到臨頭仲掛住返工，做人做到咁真係抵鳩你地班唔肯罷工既奴隸死"},{"pid":"4bfe2cab025444f7e173ac0d929ae5c8983c9b58","tid":1846992,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T23:39:44.000Z","msg":"「緊急」香港人絕不能被種族清洗！罷工上街封關！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847009</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e274a18b4db3a071bd06a9a2c740fc564a29503","tid":1846992,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T02:00:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc1dda85563143e5fcfb313cb4f32d36aa6de06a","tid":1846992,"uid":2915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}